Golden energy has two listed subsidiaries- one listed in asx (Stanmore resources) And another listed in indo stock exchange (pt golden energy mines)Go and calculate the value of golden energy stakes in these two listed subsidiaries and compared with golden energy market capitalisation in Singapore

Taking stock of GEAR' s current constituent components - GEMS Indonesia (owns 62.5%) and Stanmore Resources Australia (owns 64.1%) - their market caps are now 35.44 Tr IDR and A$2.45B respectively.
